title: Welcome!
text:
Siaa Singh



Hi, I’m Siaa 👋
I’m a senior Environmental Science major at UC Santa Barbara passionate about data-driven solutions for clean energy and environmental equity.

🌱 Intern @ California Energy Commission (Transportation Electrification)
📚 Capstone: Pico Grids as Climate Solutions
🌍 Interested in energy access, marine conservation, and climate policy

This site is a portfolio of my work and interests — feel free to explore!
